title: Peace and Love Hostel
description:
Hello! Welcome !

The Hostel is open 24 hours a day, no curfew, no lock-out. The atmosphere in the hostel is unique, you have the opportunity to meet locals in the bar. You will have good time here. It's a nice new building, recently refurbished, over looking at the canal (river). Ground floor bar with terrace open till 2.00 am. We serve more than 10 varieties of beers. Guests between the ages of 18 and 35 years only !!
